# Frontend env vars (Vite reads VITE_* into import.meta.env)
#
# Authentication
# --------------
# Clerk publishable key from https://dashboard.clerk.com → API keys.
# Leave unset (or use the placeholder) to run the web app against the API's
# dev-only mock-auth fallback — no sign-in screen, every request acts as
# `dev-user-1`. Set a real `pk_test_...` or `pk_live_...` to enable Clerk
# sign-in/up, the protected-route guard, the axios bearer interceptor, and
# the cache-clear-on-sign-out behaviour wired in src/main.tsx.
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="your_clerk_publishable_key"
